Hello new recruit! To get started read the comments of SAMSIM.f90, or look directly into documentation/Reference_manual.pdf, which was generated from the source code via doxygen. For questions contact Philipp Griewank (philipp.griewank@uni-koel.de), Niels Fuchs (niels.fuchs@awi.de), or Dirk Notz (dirk.notz@uni-koeln.de). Good luck!
